name: Selle Italia Donna Gel Flow Saddle - Women's
description: Thanks to a wider rear section, the Donna has a shape that perfectly matches the female anatomy and posture. With its streamlined shape and gel inserts, it's a high performance, comfort saddle that will let you crank when road riding or going off-road.Waterproof cover.Gel insert and anatomical cut-out for sweet comfort.Vibrations dampening ryslan and nylon base.Dimensions are 16 x 26cm.
